---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Visibility — SEO, AEO & GEO for Small Business — LeadFair"
  description="Get found on Google, in AI search results, and across the web. SEO, AEO, and GEO strategies built specifically for small businesses."
  headline="Get Found Where It Matters"
  subheadline="SEO is just the start. We make sure your business shows up on Google, in AI-powered search answers, and across the web — wherever your customers are looking."
  accentColor="secondary"
>
  <!-- What We Do -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Three Types of Visibility</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">Search is changing. People don't just Google things anymore — they ask AI. We cover all three.</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-secondary-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-secondary-100">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-secondary-800">SEO</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-secondary-600 mb-4">Search Engine Optimization</p>
          <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">The foundation. Making sure your website shows up when people search for what you offer on Google.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-light">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-secondary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              Website optimization & content
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-secondary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              Google Business Profile management
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-secondary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              Local search rankings
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-secondary-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-secondary-100">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-secondary-800">AEO</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-secondary-600 mb-4">AI Engine Optimization</p>
          <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">The new frontier. Making sure AI assistants (ChatGPT, Claude, Perplexity) recommend your business when people ask.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-light">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-secondary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              Structured data & schema markup
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-secondary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              Authoritative content strategy
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-secondary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              AI-friendly website structure
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-secondary-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-secondary-100">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-secondary-800">GEO</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-secondary-600 mb-4">Generative Engine Optimization</p>
          <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">The next wave. Optimizing your online presence so generative AI search results feature your business.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-light">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-secondary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              Cross-platform presence building
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-secondary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              Citation & mention strategy
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-secondary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              Brand authority development
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why It Matters -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-14">Why This Matters Now</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">AI Is Changing How People Find Businesses</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">More and more people are asking ChatGPT, Perplexity, and AI assistants for recommendations instead of searching Google. If your business isn't positioned for AI answers, you're becoming invisible to a growing segment of customers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Most Small Businesses Haven't Adapted</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">While big companies invest millions in AI-era search strategies, most small businesses are still stuck on basic SEO — if they're doing anything at all. That gap is an opportunity for businesses that move now.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">We Practice What We Preach</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">This very website is built using the same visibility principles we implement for clients. Fast load times, semantic HTML, structured data, authoritative content. We don't sell what we don't use.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
